We did not specifically need to remove any entries or data points, but we do have plenty of NA responses. These are dealt with by using na.rm = TRUE when finding means, standard deviation, skewness, and kurtosis of our dimensions, or with use =pairwise.complete.obs when finding 2-dimensional statistics like covariance and correlation.
